Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:10.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What do you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,m-m-mean
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.03,0:03:13.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.21,0:03:14.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I d-d-don't
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.73,0:03:15.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,understand
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:16.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,—stand —stand —stand —stand .
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.39,0:03:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:26.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm. What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.05,0:03:27.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you forgot what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:29.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even after you saw my panties.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.82,0:03:33.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After staring right at them.
