Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:34.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.12,0:03:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a misunderstanding, it's all a misunderstanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.95,0:03:40.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only saw the lining of your skirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.57,0:03:41.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:45.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was the only thing I was paying attention to—the lining of your skirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:48.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's pretty perverted in its own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.61,0:03:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanekawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.45,0:03:56.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:03:57.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:00.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Going for a walk? I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:01.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.31,0:04:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you reading Araragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.82,0:04:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that a book about baseball?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, is that book something you don't want me seeing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.01,0:04:15.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, could it be something dirty?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:16.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:21.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've never even touched printed matter as crass as that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.52,0:04:23.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want to sully my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.39,0:04:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, yep, that's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.65,0:04:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, why are you leaving so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.57,0:04:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We should take the chance to talk some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.38,0:04:50.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.98,0:04:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm? Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.77,0:04:55.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So Araragi,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.57,0:04:57.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,what did you study today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.12,0:05:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I focused mostly on math.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-Math, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.62,0:05:08.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Unfortunately, all I studied today was Spanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.77,0:05:10.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spanish?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.57,0:05:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Too bad, I don't know much Spanish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.10,0:05:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-That really is too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.87,0:05:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.60,0:05:21.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know just enough for basic conversations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.59,0:05:25.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Spasibo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:31.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Spasibo{\i} is Russian.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:36.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, {\i1}spasibo{\i} doesn't have any connotation of wonderful if you wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.02,0:05:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:40.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need to remember what words mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.74,0:05:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:44.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You really do know everything, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.38,0:05:47.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just know what I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:05:56.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.28,0:05:59.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,learning is a really great thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.04,0:06:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every day is a new lesson for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.67,0:06:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a pretty good one, Araragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:08.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So let's think about something more constructive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.68,0:06:09.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:12.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like how to make society a better place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.44,0:06:13.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.25,0:06:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, what might we do to get rid of bullying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.47,0:06:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanekawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.61,0:06:40.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you head home already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:45.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was about to do the same, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.67,0:06:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you don't have to tell me. That was my plan to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:54.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't wander around at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.30,0:06:58.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might run into a vampire, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:14.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I was kind of hoping I would.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:21.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it's only a rumor—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.95,0:07:25.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I was thinking I just might get to meet a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.58,0:07:27.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why would you want to meet a vampire?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.49,0:07:47.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I don't have anything particular in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:52.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm at that age where you hanker after something out of the ordinary, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:55.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd meet a vampire,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:57.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then have a little chat—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.94,0:07:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:02.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:04.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like I touched a nerve there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.74,0:08:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. {\i1}You're{\i0} the one who gets on my nerve.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:15.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It just pisses me off...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:17.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That arrogance of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:23.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm alone because I want to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:24.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop following me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.07,0:08:29.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-Araragi, why are you saying these things all of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.21,0:08:34.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't we having fun talking until just a second ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.57,0:08:38.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't fun for me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was only pretending it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was only after your fortune.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:48.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-My family isn't that rich, you know?
