Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.59,0:08:56.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know if this is some way for you to get good letters of recommendation,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.53,0:09:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but what's a model student like you doing talking to a washout like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:06.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You might enjoy whatever feelings of superiority you get from this,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:10.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I can't bear you standing there and feeling sorry for me.
