Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.72,0:13:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:20.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you just going to run, thrall of Heart-under-blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.38,0:13:24.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't call me weird names.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.28,0:14:29.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.75,0:16:58.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you up to, Dramaturgy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:02.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It is as it appears. I surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Smashed with that thing, with your strength, the damage would be tremendous—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.83,0:17:11.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it would take me two full days to regenerate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:15.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seem to have misunderstood something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not many vampires have the ability to heal damage instantaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.94,0:17:23.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You belong to a wholly different catergory.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.45,0:17:28.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After all, you are Heart-under-blade's thrall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:32.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In spite of the gap in raw ability,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.92,0:17:38.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought my experience gave me a chance, for now, to beat you—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:40.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it seems impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.14,0:17:43.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Netting you is beyond me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.10,0:17:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No—wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.85,0:17:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would you be satisfied, then, if I said this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will never lay my hands on you again,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:53.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so please spare my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:09.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:11.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that takes care of the right leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.40,0:18:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.78,0:18:51.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Araragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was too far away to see clearly,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.16,0:18:59.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but... weren't you just doing something out of a fantasy novel?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:01.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's it have to do with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rather,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:06.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,why are you tailing me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.26,0:19:07.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:10.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you not to follow me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.39,0:19:12.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop pretending to be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:18.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not the type to say that kind of thing, are you, Araragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.57,0:19:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I feel bad that I'm making you say these things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.30,0:19:29.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It must mean that you're in such a tough spot,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.62,0:19:32.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that your only option is to say them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.54,0:19:39.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for taking so long to notice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.87,0:19:40.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:43.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, I want to help if that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.68,0:19:47.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really pushy, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.10,0:19:52.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're reading too much into things.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.09,0:19:56.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just bored of hanging out with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:59.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I prefer to be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.48,0:20:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.54,0:20:06.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're not a misanthrope or the world-weary type, Araragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.84,0:20:08.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can figure that much out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:09.14,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\alpha&H50&\blur6}Flashback
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.97,0:20:09.14,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.001}Flashback
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.64,0:20:11.82,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\alpha&H50&\blur6}Flashback
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.64,0:20:11.82,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.001}Flashback
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.58,0:20:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At least, you seemed to be having fun when you were talking to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.56,0:20:19.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I was only after your fortune!
Comment: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kanji FIX
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:16.40,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,255)\fscx150\fscy150\alpha&H50&\blur7.5}Like I said
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.86,0:20:16.40,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,255)\fscx150\fscy150\blur1.001}Like I said
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.10,0:20:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And like I said, my family isn't that rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.23,0:20:19.73,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,255)\fscx150\fscy150\alpha&H50&\blur7.5}Like I said
Dialogue: 1,0:20:19.23,0:20:19.73,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,255)\fscx150\fscy150\blur1.001}Like I said
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:32.25,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,255)\fscx150\fscy150\alpha&H50&\blur7.5}Like I said
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.00,0:20:32.25,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,255)\fscx150\fscy150\blur1.001}Like I said
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.29,0:20:24.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I was only after your toddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:30.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't drink, and you shouldn't either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:32.83,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,255)\fscx150\fscy150\alpha&H50&\blur7.5}Body
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.58,0:20:32.83,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,255)\fscx150\fscy150\blur1.001}Body
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.26,0:20:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm telling you I was only after your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.18,0:20:36.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which is it, my toddy or my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.15,0:20:37.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fine then, I'll make up with you if you show me your panties again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.37,0:20:52.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:27.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you see them all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.95,0:21:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to take off my blouse, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:36.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.07,0:21:41.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I said some horrible things. I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.93,0:21:56.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.12,0:22:23.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He really did give it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.43,0:22:26.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what a negotiator is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.60,0:22:29.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, Heart-under-blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, what are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:37.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That leg doesn't match your current size.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.37,0:22:40.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You aren't just swapping them, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:42.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.36,0:22:55.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't be standing there gaping, fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.37,0:22:57.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave me to myself as I eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.47,0:22:59.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are thy manners?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.24,0:23:06.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, Oshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:09.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.99,0:23:11.49,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\alpha&H50&\blur6}Flashback
Dialogue: 1,0:23:10.99,0:23:11.49,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.001}Flashback
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.68,0:23:16.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My left arm was blown clean off by Dramaturgy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.67,0:23:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I recovered instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.94,0:23:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So why didn't Kiss-shot's limbs regenerate at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.38,0:23:23.63,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\alpha&H50&\blur6}Flashback
Dialogue: 1,0:23:23.38,0:23:23.63,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.001}Flashback
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.44,0:23:31.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think it's because Heart-under-blade
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.30,0:23:35.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,had lost nearly all of her immortal force by the time you met her?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.45,0:23:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.85,0:23:41.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, yes, I did think of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.97,0:23:44.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But during my fight,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.44,0:23:44.69,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\alpha&H50&\blur6}Flashback
Dialogue: 1,0:23:44.44,0:23:44.69,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.001}Flashback
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:49.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when my arms were cut off,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.05,0:23:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the old ones disappeared by the time I was healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.83,0:23:58.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I thought maybe Kiss-shot's limbs might have disappeared, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.82,0:24:00.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that wasn't the case either.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.36,0:24:03.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, how come—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.34,0:24:06.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they didn't regenerate, and they didn't disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.58,0:24:10.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That kid is a rare breed, Araragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.01,0:24:16.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those guys wanted her body intact—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.37,0:24:17.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to steal it and make it their own.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.33,0:24:24.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those guys divided the body from the limbs did they not?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.55,0:24:29.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, it wasn't her limbs that they took from her,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.74,0:24:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but also her existence as a vampire itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.26,0:24:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oshino.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.69,0:24:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.26,0:24:40.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,really going to be able to become human again?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.53,0:24:46.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't see why not, as long as you can get back all of Heart-under-blade's arms and legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.21,0:24:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what the kid said?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.21,0:24:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the thing,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.03,0:24:54.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,isn't there the possibility that Kiss-shot is lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.93,0:24:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can see how she might be in order to get her limbs—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.00,0:24:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.33,0:25:04.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't distrust her like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.38,0:25:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Poor girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.19,0:25:07.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.57,0:25:11.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Saying that about someone who saved your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.67,0:25:13.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't believe how ungrateful you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.08,0:25:22.25,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\alpha&H50&\blur6}Flashback
Dialogue: 1,0:25:22.08,0:25:22.25,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.001}Flashback
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.58,0:25:31.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with that face, Araragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.89,0:25:34.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something good happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.64,0:25:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't talk like you see through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.94,0:26:33.94,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,285)\fscx115\fscy115\alpha&H50&\blur9}April 1st
Dialogue: 1,0:26:31.94,0:26:33.94,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,285)\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.001}April 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.77,0:27:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So maybe... it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.53,0:27:17.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.33,0:27:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.49,0:27:22.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your run-in with a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.51,0:27:27.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rumors have a funny way of coming true, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.16,0:27:32.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially for ghost stories and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.52,0:27:38.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They say {\i1}rumoring{\i} has a way of—having them find their way to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.77,0:27:41.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.21,0:27:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You told me about the rumor, so you'd have to run into a vampire too.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.03,0:27:51.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't {\i1}have{\i} to,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.08,0:27:55.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's probably just that your chances increase...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.84,0:28:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, I have, haven't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.14,0:28:03.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You, Araragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.29,0:28:09.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Putting the talk about rumors aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.73,0:28:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,yesterday you were going out of your way to look for a vampire, if anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.82,0:28:18.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.17,0:28:24.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you wanted to talk to one or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.00,0:28:29.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it wasn't that I was seriously looking for a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.27,0:28:32.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was stamping my feet for something that I know doesn't exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.14,0:28:34.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How do I say this?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.88,0:28:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I've been going in circles and wanted a change in my life?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.29,0:28:41.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haven't you ever wanted a change in your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.72,0:28:43.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A change, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.57,0:28:46.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just my way of trying to escape from reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.33,0:28:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd love to get back to reality, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.15,0:28:52.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll be able to.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.12,0:29:04.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like I said, I want to help,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.49,0:29:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but considering how outrageous this situation is,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.68,0:29:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it doesn't feel like there's much I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.68,0:29:13.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.51,0:29:19.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those clothes and daily essentials are a great help.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.91,0:29:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.88,0:29:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you hurry up and get changed, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.38,0:29:27.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your clothes are a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.68,0:29:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.28,0:29:30.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.48,0:29:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.28,0:29:37.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess I could at least change my shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.49,0:29:42.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was medium okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.14,0:29:44.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.80,0:29:48.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't know which you wanted, so I got you both boxers and briefs.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.33,0:29:52.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.95,0:29:54.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not going to change?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.53,0:29:55.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.10,0:30:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.86,0:30:17.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.31,0:30:19.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought so yesteday too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.34,0:30:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your body's a little different, Araragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.26,0:30:30.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something seemed a bit off when I saw you from behind yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.75,0:30:33.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So it was your muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.67,0:30:37.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You also seem thinner, more cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.34,0:30:44.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course thy body has changed, ye've become a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.43,0:30:50.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Our powers of healing work to keep our bodies in optimal condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.94,0:30:58.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.36,0:31:03.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just from touching though,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.90,0:31:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,you still feel the same as other humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.28,0:31:10.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But with subtly more muscle elasticity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.84,0:31:13.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The same as other humans?"
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.56,0:31:17.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanekawa, does that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.30,0:31:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've touched the bodies of other men?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.56,0:31:22.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.58,0:31:24.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way I would do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.89,0:31:29.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Th-That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.71,0:31:32.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was speaking from imagination, not experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.50,0:31:34.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.15,0:31:40.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and put on that shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.07,0:31:41.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.34,0:31:55.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks great on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.80,0:32:00.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for all the help, Hanekawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.97,0:32:03.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll definitely pay you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.82,0:32:10.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have to. This is really all I can do, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.69,0:32:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All you can do? It's more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.28,0:32:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you. I mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.11,0:32:21.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.95,0:32:24.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what friends are for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.28,0:32:35.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't hesitate to let me know
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.03,0:32:38.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if there's anything else you want me to do, Araragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.25,0:32:42.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is about everything I can do at the moment, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.99,0:32:48.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Do you want me to clean this classroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.70,0:32:50.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like a total mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.01,0:32:53.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine. It was like this when we found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.10,0:32:58.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's no reason to leave it a mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.77,0:33:01.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We ought to start where we can, and—
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.48,0:33:04.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.51,0:33:05.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.45,0:33:07.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.04,0:33:08.30,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\alpha&H50&\blur6}Flashback
Dialogue: 1,0:33:08.04,0:33:08.30,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.001}Flashback
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.21,0:33:09.35,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\alpha&H50&\blur6}Flashback
Dialogue: 1,0:33:09.21,0:33:09.35,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.001}Flashback
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.10,0:33:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had forgotten to tell thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.44,0:33:18.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That bag thou had so preciously clung to was on the side of the station,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.60,0:33:22.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I brought it here with me for thee.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.79,0:33:24.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You goddamned traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.74,0:33:28.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.38,0:33:32.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you encountered that vampire, you were...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.67,0:33:35.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,on the way back from the bookstore, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.31,0:33:38.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On March 25th?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.29,0:33:42.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The night of the day we first ran into each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.79,0:33:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.38,0:33:51.39,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,285)\fscx115\fscy115\alpha&H50&\blur6}April 4th
Dialogue: 1,0:33:49.38,0:33:51.39,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,285)\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.001}April 4th
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.53,0:33:59.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Episode is a half-vampire vampire hunter...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.76,0:34:01.27,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,600)\fscx115\fscy115\alpha&H50&\blur6}Flashback End
Dialogue: 1,0:34:00.76,0:34:01.27,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,600)\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.001}Flashback End
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.67,0:34:06.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, even I know that much vampire terminology,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.77,0:34:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but couldn't you give me some more details, Kiss-shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.10,0:34:13.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.34,0:34:25.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.61,0:34:28.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One moment. I'll remember in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.02,0:34:34.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.71,0:34:36.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What did you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.98,0:34:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Episode fellow...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.45,0:34:41.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,detests vampires with a passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.84,0:34:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He detests them?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.68,0:34:44.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.32,0:34:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's half vampire, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.20,0:34:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, to put it simply,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.89,0:34:56.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,'tis because half-vampires are not accepted into the world of vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.59,0:35:01.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nor is that reason enough for them to be accepted into the human world.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.18,0:35:03.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.38,0:35:06.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,they hate their vampire blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.61,0:35:12.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Episode in particular seems to have a strong hatred of vampires.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.77,0:35:18.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While work may have driven Dramaturgy, emotions move Episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.13,0:35:37.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotta love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.99,0:35:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cracks me up, it really does.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.08,0:35:45.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Old Dramaturgy finding himself on the wrong end of a hunt going after a brat like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.84,0:35:52.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll show those guys how to hunt their prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.61,0:36:01.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm warning you,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.19,0:36:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,don't think I'll go easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.34,0:36:07.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hate picking on the weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.71,0:36:10.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but I love picking on the evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.41,0:36:12.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.73,0:36:15.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.24,0:36:17.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.48,0:36:18.74,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,255)\fscx150\fscy150\alpha&H50&\blur7.5}Monster
Dialogue: 1,0:36:18.48,0:36:18.74,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,255)\fscx150\fscy150\blur1}Monster
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.59,0:36:21.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you—
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.21,0:36:23.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.44,0:36:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't I what?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.08,0:36:28.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there's something you want to say, spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.19,0:36:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.32,0:36:33.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I want to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.61,0:36:36.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get started.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.31,0:37:34.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C-Cross?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.73,0:38:56.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Araragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.84,0:39:01.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't give up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.89,0:39:04.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The opponent turns into mist—
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.38,0:39:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He turns into mist, so that means—
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.62,0:39:14.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanekawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.90,0:39:33.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanekawa, Hanekawa, Hanekawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.05,0:39:41.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be quiet, Araragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.47,0:39:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get it together...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.49,0:39:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're dealing with mist.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.17,0:39:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gotta love it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.91,0:40:41.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mist, in other words, water.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.00,0:40:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What would happen if I dumped sand on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.69,0:41:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay, enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.94,0:41:14.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Keep going and you won't be a human anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.12,0:41:19.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,O-Oshi— O—
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.53,0:41:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You were—
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.35,0:41:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What about Hanekawa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.58,0:41:24.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't yell.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.73,0:41:27.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So spirited, Araragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.89,0:41:29.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something good happen to you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.44,0:41:31.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.55,0:41:33.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to dampen your spirits,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.69,0:41:35.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but the fight's been decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.12,0:41:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just look, he's passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.52,0:41:47.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... but...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.76,0:41:50.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanekawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.19,0:41:56.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanekawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.35,0:42:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanekawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.69,0:42:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.56,0:42:05.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw? But why—
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.91,0:42:09.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you stop her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.45,0:42:11.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not included in the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.10,0:42:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've only taken on negotiating with three vampire hunters.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.43,0:42:20.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anything beyond that requires a separate fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.15,0:42:22.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't get mixed up with ordinary people.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.58,0:42:30.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then tell me that from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.22,0:42:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you had—
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.52,0:42:38.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You could pay for missy class president's fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.24,0:42:40.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about another two million?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.92,0:42:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two million?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.49,0:42:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I would've paid three!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.77,0:42:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't a game, Oshino!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.79,0:42:55.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's no game. It's about gain, Araragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.79,0:42:52.43,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,255)\fscx150\fscy150\alpha&H50&\blur7.5}Game
Dialogue: 1,0:42:51.79,0:42:52.43,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,255)\fscx150\fscy150\blur1.001}Game
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.92,0:42:53.56,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,255)\fscx150\fscy150\alpha&H50&\blur7.5}Gain
Dialogue: 1,0:42:52.92,0:42:53.56,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,255)\fscx150\fscy150\blur1.001}Gain
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.64,0:42:58.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We have a deal. Three million yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.94,0:43:01.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll give you a hint, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.92,0:43:05.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Try using your head, Araragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.08,0:43:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that immortal body of yours for?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.48,0:43:51.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanekawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.26,0:43:58.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Araragi?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.60,0:44:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why are you rubbing your cheek against my stomach, and so fondly too?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.42,0:44:12.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, my uniform is torn.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.46,0:44:14.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should I chalk that up to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.39,0:44:16.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My bad, Hanekawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.84,0:44:21.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay still for a bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.27,0:45:18.28,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,285)\fscx115\fscy115\alpha&H50&\blur6}April 5th
Dialogue: 1,0:45:16.27,0:45:18.28,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,285)\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.001}April 5th
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.66,0:45:23.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My body feels quite a bit better.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.78,0:45:29.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I dare say that my immortality has nearly returned.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.88,0:45:33.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh... so are you at a point where you might, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.54,0:45:35.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,take care of the next battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.32,0:45:41.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, I seem as yet unable to use my skills as a vampire.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.41,0:45:46.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has become harder for me to die, but that is the extent of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.08,0:45:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perhaps I would be able to fight Dramaturgy,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.22,0:45:53.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but even Episode might prove too much for my current state.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.26,0:45:57.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let alone Guillotine Cutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.15,0:46:01.28,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\alpha&H50&\blur6}Flashback
Dialogue: 1,0:45:59.15,0:46:01.28,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.001}Flashback
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.15,0:46:01.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Guillotine Cutter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.03,0:46:04.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Am I right to think that he's human?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.10,0:46:09.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Indeed. He is neither a vampire like Dramaturgy,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.05,0:46:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,nor a half-vampire like Episode.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.53,0:46:11.67,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\alpha&H50&\blur6}Flashback
Dialogue: 1,0:46:11.53,0:46:11.67,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.001}Flashback
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.02,0:46:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He is a plain, pure and simple, human.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.97,0:46:19.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He didn't seem all that plain to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.94,0:46:22.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mm. True.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.00,0:46:27.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's what ye'd call... a holy man.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.38,0:46:33.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he's some kind of Christian spec ops.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.62,0:46:35.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So close, yet so far.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.46,0:46:38.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But... whatever else he may be, he's still a human, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.15,0:46:43.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No matter what methods he uses, won't he still be no match for a vampire?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.79,0:46:49.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Neither a vampire, nor a half-vampire,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.72,0:46:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but a human has taken on vampire hunting as his specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.24,0:46:55.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If anything, it should be cause for concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.08,0:47:00.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In fact, has he not taken both my arms from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.10,0:47:05.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Still, it was because I erred in not taking them seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.93,0:47:08.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I felt a tad under the weather, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.52,0:47:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If work is what drives Dramaturgy,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.51,0:47:15.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and emotions Episode,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.21,0:47:18.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then 'tis duty that spurs Guillotine Cutter.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.39,0:47:23.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As odd as it is for me to say this, faith is quite a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.54,0:47:30.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanekawa, how's the wound on your stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.60,0:47:32.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The wound—well,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.49,0:47:34.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there's nothing left of the wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.44,0:47:36.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.12,0:47:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.02,0:47:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What 'here'?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.33,0:47:52.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Araragi-kun, would you like a sandwich?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.65,0:47:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This one has tomato.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.68,0:47:58.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.64,0:47:59.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.74,0:48:07.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, Araragi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.20,0:48:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Coca Cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.39,0:48:10.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.31,0:48:15.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And for me, I have Diet Cola.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.85,0:48:19.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If your body naturally puts on muscle,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.41,0:48:23.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,does that mean you can take as many calories as you want without getting fat.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.57,0:48:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That'd make any girl jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.65,0:48:30.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.95,0:48:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If anything, it's that I don't feel hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.95,0:48:38.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like, I'd be fine if I didn't eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.34,0:48:41.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't vampires feed on blood for their meals?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.26,0:48:43.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.63,0:48:52.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speaking of, Araragi. Do you ever get urges to suck blood or anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.00,0:48:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.16,0:48:56.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, now that you mention it, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.23,0:49:09.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanekawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.76,0:49:17.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should stop coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.50,0:49:26.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought you might say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.50,0:49:29.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, I don't want you to feel hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.78,0:49:31.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,it's not like last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.26,0:49:33.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.68,0:49:37.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was partly about not wanting to get you mixed up in it, of course,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.09,0:49:42.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but a lot of it was my not being able to keep my emotions in check.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.98,0:49:46.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I took it out on you, and I regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.21,0:49:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this time is different.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.36,0:49:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's it different?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:53.34,0:49:57.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When Episode's cross took a chunk out of your side yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.74,0:50:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I lost myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.76,0:50:01.89,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\alpha&H50&\blur6}Flashback
Dialogue: 1,0:50:01.76,0:50:01.89,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,337.5)\fscx115\fscy115\blur1.001}Flashback
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.18,0:50:04.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I could feel the blood rising to my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.55,0:50:05.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.54,0:50:09.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.36,0:50:12.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.70,0:50:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I talked to you about my intensity as a human, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.24,0:50:25.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You getting wounded hurt like it was me who'd gotten wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.13,0:50:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No—
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.27,0:50:29.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It hurt more.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.11,0:50:31.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanekawa, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.53,0:50:37.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not so desperate to become a human again that I'd do it at your expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.79,0:50:39.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At my expense?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.58,0:50:49.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't feel like you're treating me in such a way, Araragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.59,0:50:52.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But don't you wonder what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.04,0:50:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wasting your spring break for my sake
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.20,0:50:57.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,at an important time in your life—
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.89,0:51:00.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And nearly dying in the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.31,0:51:02.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that make you wonder what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.68,0:51:04.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-Not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.44,0:51:08.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.09,0:51:14.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not confident that I'd be able to help you in the same situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.59,0:51:17.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't be able to go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.78,0:51:21.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Showing myself to a loose cannon like him—
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.11,0:51:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if I had a body that could die—
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.45,0:51:30.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you did it like it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.12,0:51:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.98,0:51:33.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,scare me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:37.71,0:51:39.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're too bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.56,0:51:47.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't sacrifice yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.04,0:51:49.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please, I'm not saying that to hurt you,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.18,0:51:54.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just can't understand why you're going this far for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.46,0:51:56.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't figure it out,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.51,0:51:58.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,how you'd be this devoted
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.28,0:52:02.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to a classmate you only got to know the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.78,0:52:06.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's like you're a saint.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.13,0:52:13.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But your self-sacrifice is way too heavy a burden for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.75,0:52:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not big enough to bear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.10,0:52:21.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not self-sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.77,0:52:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It {\i1}isn't{\i} self-sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.72,0:52:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.39,0:52:29.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Self-satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.66,0:52:36.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're misunderstanding me, Araragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.63,0:52:42.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not that good of a person, and I'm not that strong of a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.36,0:52:46.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just doing what ever I feel like doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:47.16,0:52:52.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt there are many people out there as self-absorbed as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.32,0:52:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sneaky, and I think I'm tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.72,0:53:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Enough to creep you out, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.22,0:53:05.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.37,0:53:09.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,if my presence is making things harder for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.75,0:53:13.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then that really is putting the cart before the horse.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.89,0:53:19.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you say so, then it must be time I leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.32,0:53:25.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It does look like there's nothing left for me to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.75,0:53:29.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, there is something you can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.69,0:53:31.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.00,0:53:34.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that school, once the new year starts.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.80,0:53:36.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.53,0:53:42.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward with all my heart to chatting with you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:51.52,0:53:52.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that the sound of?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.12,0:53:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My hearth throbbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.66,0:53:58.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Girls come with a sound effect for that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.00,0:54:01.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.64,0:54:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I nearly developed something for you just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.59,0:54:07.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do we mean by 'developed' here, like a new drug or a beach resort?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.73,0:54:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's the line you use to sweet-talk girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.33,0:54:13.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No no. I don't even know what you mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.83,0:54:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I barely even talk to girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.80,0:54:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen to you, acting all tough and uninterested. Like you never bought those dirty magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.25,0:54:26.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.51,0:54:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll let you borrow these.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.90,0:54:49.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give them back when we meet next school year.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:52.24,0:54:55.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Araragi, you like panties, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.71,0:54:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.35,0:55:00.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you don't want them—
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.28,0:55:03.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.13,0:55:04.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I never said I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.24,0:55:07.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wanting it or not isn't the issue here, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.07,0:55:09.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.37,0:55:12.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I give these back to you when we meet next school year, right?!
Comment: 0,0:55:16.45,0:55:18.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sound Effect FIX
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.90,0:55:19.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.00,0:55:21.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't give these back.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.01,0:55:22.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:23.46,0:55:25.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I mean, I'm never giving these back.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.11,0:55:30.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm passing these down from generation to generation as the Araragi family heirloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.66,0:55:32.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I certainly didn't sign up for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.46,0:55:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These panties have parted from your flesh for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.75,0:55:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.49,0:55:40.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I won't give them back,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.78,0:55:41.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but mark my words.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:42.69,0:55:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I will return this favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.02,0:55:46.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there's ever a time you need me,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.18,0:55:49.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and even if there's nothing I can do,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.51,0:55:52.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.28,0:55:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As of today, it will be my life's mission
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.20,0:55:58.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,to repay you.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.78,0:56:03.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just give my panties back!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.19,0:56:23.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, now I'm going to have to go home,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.81,0:56:27.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,panty-less, and in a skirt,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.55,0:56:30.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with its low security rating.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.03,0:56:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Araragi, compared to that, beating this Guillotine Cutter person
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.03,0:56:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,can't be that hard, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.38,0:56:45.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Point taken!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.57,0:56:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.81,0:56:57.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.17,0:57:06.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until next school year.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.82,0:57:09.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until next school year.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.42,0:57:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I messed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.11,0:57:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Missy class president got kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.26,0:57:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.05,0:57:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it that I need to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.72,0:57:58.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Araragi,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.64,0:58:02.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,forget about your humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.08,0:58:05.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Araragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.70,0:58:08.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Araragi. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.10,0:58:22.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do to Hanekawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.64,0:58:24.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not going to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.77,0:58:27.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.30,0:58:32.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While I may not have superhuman strength like your kind,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.72,0:58:35.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have trained quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.18,0:58:37.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A single girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.59,0:58:39.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Killing her would be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.38,0:58:44.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you call yourself human?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.37,0:58:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hanekawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.92,0:58:55.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.62,0:59:00.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:01.92,0:59:04.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.19,0:59:10.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am not so tolerant as to allow myself to a be a willing participant in your show of high school friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.98,0:59:12.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let it begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.26,0:59:15.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.62,0:59:17.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.15,0:59:24.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All you need to do is put your hands up and say 'I give up' the moment the battle begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.61,0:59:29.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the match will be decided as soon as it begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.53,0:59:31.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:34.32,0:59:35.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Araragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.53,0:59:37.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't need to care about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.12,0:59:39.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could I not care about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:59:40.24,0:59:42.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.11,0:59:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not so desperate to become human again that I'd do it at your expense.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:47.94,0:59:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Araragi,
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.03,0:59:51.66,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,285)\fscx115\fscy115\alpha&H50&\blur6}forget about your humanity
Dialogue: 1,0:59:49.03,0:59:51.66,Black and Red,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,285)\fscx115\fscy115\blur0.85}forget about your humanity
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.40,1:01:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Looking at myself...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.20,1:01:04.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I certainly wasn't human.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.06,1:01:07.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had abandoned my humanity.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.58,1:01:10.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That much I understood.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.60,1:01:13.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was already—{\i}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.52,1:01:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a monster.{\i}
